(1175, 1, '2020-03-18 15:57:11', '2020-03-18 15:57:11', '[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"1181\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][ultimate_heading alignment=\"left\" margin_design_tab_text=\"\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A <em>guitar amplifier</em> (or <em>amp</em>) is an electronic device or system that strengthens the weak electrical signal from a pickup on an electric <em>guitar</em>, bass <em>guitar</em>, or acoustic <em>guitar</em> so that it can produce sound through one or more loudspeakers, which are typically housed in a wooden cabinet.</p>\r\n[/ultimate_heading][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"1182\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][ultimate_heading alignment=\"left\" margin_design_tab_text=\"\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A <em>guitar amplifier</em> (or <em>amp</em>) is an electronic device or system that strengthens the weak electrical signal from a pickup on an electric <em>guitar</em>, bass <em>guitar</em>, or acoustic <em>guitar</em> so that it can produce sound through one or more loudspeakers, which are typically housed in a wooden cabinet.</p>\r\n[/ultimate_heading][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"1183\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][ultimate_heading alignment=\"left\" margin_design_tab_text=\"\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A <em>guitar amplifier</em> (or <em>amp</em>) is an electronic device or system that strengthens the weak electrical signal from a pickup on an electric <em>guitar</em>, bass <em>guitar</em>, or acoustic <em>guitar</em> so that it can produce sound through one or more loudspeakers, which are typically housed in a wooden cabinet.</p>\r\n[/ultimate_heading][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"1184\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][ultimate_heading alignment=\"left\" margin_design_tab_text=\"\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A